   "body" : "If you find a block (esp p2pool users who are often behind low-upload connections) you simultaneously announce it to all peers, resulting in increased upload time and in some cases, possibly even increased orphan rate.  Bitcoin should ideally stagger uploads so that it can start getting new blocks out to the network quickly.",
